cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.RO, cs.SY, cs.CV 

The paper proposes a modification to a deep RL algorithm, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The focus on safety constraints and forbidden actions suggests relevance to robotics (cs.RO) and control systems (cs.SY). The experiments involve visual environments, indicating potential relevance to computer vision (cs.CV).
